# SmartOps environment variables
#
# The front-end works with NO env vars — it falls back to the built-in mock
# (lib/mock.ts) so dev/preview always responds.
#
# To use Ahmer's REAL 5-LLM + Critic backend, set ONE variable to the URL of his
# deployed FastAPI service (repo: github.com/ahmer64-sketch/smartops-backend):
#
#   ASSISTANT_BACKEND_URL=https://<ahmers-backend-host>/assistant
#
# Locally, if you run his backend (`uvicorn server:app --port 8000`):
#   ASSISTANT_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:8000/assistant
#
# NOTE: the ANTHROPIC_API_KEY / OPENAI_API_KEY that his pipeline needs live in
# HIS backend's host env, NOT here — this front-end never calls an LLM directly.
